'''Tusquittee Township''' is farthest north [[Township]], and one of the six townships of [[Clay County, North Carolina|Clay County]], [[North Carolina]], [[United States]]. The other five are Brasstown, Hayesville, Sweetwater, Hiawassee, and Shooting Creek.

